      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-black/50 border border-yellow-500/20 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-yellow-400/40 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
        <div class="text-yellow-400 text-4xl mb-4">
          <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Web Development</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
